Commentary.ab:
Y10.4a vərəziiaŋhuuąm] Geldner, cod.; Kellens vərəziiaŋᵛhąm; Pirart varəzi.aŋhuuąm. Cf. vərəziiaŋᵛhahe  (Y1.14, 3.15, 7.17), 
            vərəziiaŋᵛhā̊ŋhō  (Y10.14). The preservation of °ŋhuu° is regular in sveral cases: before ą, cf. aŋhuuąm (VS18.21), vaŋhuuąm (VS22.1, 8);
            after ō in derivatives of -ah stems,cf. aōjōŋhuuaṇt- and raōcōŋhuuaṇt-.
